<google-map height="500px" width="100%" [center]="{lat: 43.6532, lng: -79.3832}">
    <map-marker *ngFor="let marker of markers" [position]="{lat: marker.latitude, lng: marker.longitude}" >
        <map-info-window>{{ marker.title }}</map-info-window>
      </map-marker>
  </google-map>
